race.comment: WEST ON HALO (1) was below best last time when fifth at Mandurah but prior to that among the placings in quick time (17.34) at Mandurah. Can make amends this time. SECURITY SPOT (3) comes off an average run last start when sixth at Mandurah over 400m behind Geordie Lad (23.13) in a Grade 5/6. Expected to feature in the finish. SPEEDY DEVILLE (8) jumped from the inside and boxed on well to finish second last time, beaten 1.3 lengths (17.37) behind Aeroplane Penny at Mandurah. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card last start despite being beaten. Leading chance. NEVADA TEASE (2) is always a threat when she draws this box.
